eu.amidst.core.variables

Class Variables

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.core.variables.Variables
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<Variable>

    public class Variables
extends Object
implements Iterable<Variable>, Serializable
    This class is used to store and to handle the creation of all the variables of a Bayesian network model.

    For an example of use follow this link

    http://amidst.github.io/toolbox/CodeExamples.html#variablesexample

    See Also:
